My recommendation: The Black Forrest Sandwich.
A giant Bavarian pretzel roll topped with grilled turkey, applewood bacon, Monterey Jack cheese, shredded lettuce, sliced tomatoes and honey mustard dressing.
If you want to spice it up a bit, substitute the honey mustard for some of Fox's amazing queso dip.
A must visit.
